          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>10 users x $18/mo</span><span class="font-medium">$180/month</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 1</span><span class="font-medium">$2,160</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 2</span><span class="font-medium">$2,160</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 3</span><span class="font-medium">$2,160</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-3">
            <p class="flex justify-between font-bold text-lg"><span>3-Year Total</span><span class="text-red-600">$6,480</span></p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Based on publicly available pricing estimates. Actual pricing may vary by plan and contract.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-emerald-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 text-lg mb-4">SMBCyberHub Pro Kit</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Pro Kit (unlimited users)</span><span class="font-medium">€99</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 1 renewal</span><span class="font-medium">€0</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 2 renewal</span><span class="font-medium">€0</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>Year 3 renewal</span><span class="font-medium">€0</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="border-t border-emerald-200 pt-3">
            <p class="flex justify-between font-bold text-lg"><span>3-Year Total</span><span class="text-emerald-600">€99</span></p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">One-time purchase. No subscriptions. No per-user fees. Use with your entire team forever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-6 text-sm">That's a potential saving of over <strong>$6,000</strong> across three years for a 10-person team.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
      <blockquote class="text-gray-700 italic text-lg mb-3">"All done in one afternoon. No logins, no subscriptions, just what we needed for our cyber insurance."</blockquote>
      <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium text-sm">— Anna F, Cafe Owner, Boston</p>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">Who Should Choose KnowBe4</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">KnowBe4 is a genuinely strong platform, and it's the right fit if your organisation:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Has <strong>25+ employees</strong> and needs ongoing simulated phishing campaigns</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Has a <strong>dedicated IT team</strong> to manage the platform</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Requires <strong>granular analytics and reporting</strong> for compliance officers</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Has the <strong>budget for annual SaaS subscriptions</strong> with per-user pricing</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">Who Should Choose SMBCyberHub</h2>
      <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-emerald-200">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">SMBCyberHub is built specifically for small teams that need to get compliant without the overhead:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Run a <strong>team of 1–20 people</strong> and need compliance training done this week</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Have <strong>no dedicated IT staff</strong> — the office manager or owner handles compliance</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Need <strong>audit-ready documentation</strong> for cyber insurance or a GDPR audit</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Want a <strong>privacy-first approach</strong> — no employee data uploaded to any cloud platform</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg><span>Prefer a <strong>one-time purchase</strong> — no monthly bills, no cancellation fees</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 text-sm">Try our <a href="/free-cyber-security-training/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">free training sample</a> to see the quality before you buy.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">What's in the SMBCyberHub Pro Kit</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">The <a href="/pro-cybersecurity-kit/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Pro Kit (€99)</a> is our most complete compliance package:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Training &amp; Assessment</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
            <li>6 training modules (Phishing, Passwords, Device Security, MFA, Social Engineering, Ransomware)</li>
            <li>6 staff quizzes with answer keys</li>
            <li>Signed training log templates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Policies &amp; Documentation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
            <li>Acceptable use, incident response, and backup policies</li>
            <li>GDPR awareness documentation</li>
            <li>Security self-audit checklists</li>
            <li>Onboarding security guide</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
      <blockquote class="text-gray-700 italic text-lg mb-3">"Our insurance broker was chasing us for proof of training, but I had no idea what they wanted. The SMBCyberHub kit saved hours and made our renewal painless."</blockquote>
      <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium text-sm">— Emma P, Office Manager, London</p>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is SMBCyberHub as good as KnowBe4?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">They serve different markets. KnowBe4 is an enterprise-grade platform with active phishing simulations designed for large organisations with dedicated IT teams. SMBCyberHub provides downloadable compliance kits purpose-built for small teams of 1–20 people who need to get compliant quickly without managing a SaaS platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I switch from KnowBe4 to SMBCyberHub?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes. SMBCyberHub kits are standalone downloadable files. You can purchase a kit, run your training, and have audit-ready documentation the same day — no migration or data transfer needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do insurers accept SMBCyberHub documentation?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes. Our kits include signed training logs, quiz records, policy templates, and checklists aligned with NIST and GDPR frameworks. These are the same types of documentation cyber insurance underwriters request during renewals and audits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Does SMBCyberHub include phishing simulations?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">No. SMBCyberHub focuses on compliance documentation, staff training materials, and audit readiness. If your primary need is simulated phishing campaigns for a large workforce, KnowBe4 is more appropriate. If you need affordable compliance training and documentation for a small team, SMBCyberHub is the practical choice.</p>
