    <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">KnowBe4 is a world-class security awareness platform — and if you're a 200-person company with an IT department, it deserves to be on your shortlist. But most small businesses don't need simulated phishing campaigns, LMS dashboards, or annual SaaS contracts.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">What they need is a fast, affordable way to train their team, document their policies, and satisfy their insurer — all without creating new vendor dependencies or uploading employee data to another cloud platform. That's what <a href="/kits/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">SMBCyberHub kits</a> deliver.</p>
