    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Ready to Get Compliant — Without the Complexity?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Start with our free training sample or go straight to the Pro Kit for complete coverage.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/free-cyber-security-training/" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transform hover:scale-105 transition">Try Free Training Sample</a>
        <a href="/kits/" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transform hover:scale-105 transition">Compare Kits &amp; Pricing</a>
